OL,4,Cand battered' guilty of manslaughter
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,7,Fsome readers may find distressing
OL,9,FA dad has been found guilty of killing
OL,10,Fhis six-month-old son, who prosecutors
OL,11,Fsaid was "shaken and battered" before
OL,12,Fhe died.
OL,14,FDavid Hollick, 29, denied murder and
OL,15,Fan alternative charge of manslaughter
OL,16,Fin connection with the death of baby
OL,17,FKairo Jax Hollick, who died at on
OL,18,FFebruary 12 2020, days after suffering
OL,19,Fa "non-survivable brain injury."
