OL,6,FA jury of 10 women and two men took
OL,7,Faround 20 hours to find Hollick, from
OL,8,F, not guilty of murder but guilty of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter by a majority of 11 to
OL,10,Fone on Monday afternoon.
OL,12,FThe trial heard that as well as the
OL,13,Fbrain injury, Kairo had suffered at
OL,14,Fleast two skull fractures and a
OL,15,Ffracture to his right arm while he was
OL,16,Fin the care of his father on 9
OL,17,FFebruary.
