OL,6,FProsecutor David Mason KC told the
OL,7,Fcourt Kairo "had not only been shaken
OL,8,Fviolently, but his head had been
OL,9,Fbashed at least twice" with a hard
OL,10,Fobject by Hollick.
OL,12,FThere were sobs from the public
OL,13,Fgallery as the verdicts were handed
OL,14,Fdown to Hollick, who sat with his head
OL,15,Fin his hands.
