OL,6,FThe trial had heard Hollick's ex-
OL,7,Fpartner Adina Johnson had dropped
OL,8,Ftheir son off at his home as usual on
OL,9,F7 February for the weekend and while
OL,10,FKairo had a cold at the time, she had
OL,11,Fno other concerns about his health.
OL,13,FHollick was staying in the
OL,14,Fconservatory at his parents' home due
OL,15,Fto a lack of bedroom space after
OL,16,Fmoving back in with them when his
OL,17,Frelationship with Ms Johnson ended.
