OL,4,Cand battered' guilty of manslaughter
OL,6,FThe court heard Hollick phoned Ms
OL,7,FJohnson at 4.30am on 9 February, but
OL,8,Fshe did not answer because of the
OL,9,Ftime, instead messaging him to say she
OL,10,Fwould call him back later on.
OL,12,FHollick immediately sent her a message
OL,13,Ftelling her to "ring him back, it's
OL,14,Fabout Kai".
OL,16,FThe last person to see Kairo alive and
OL,17,Fwell was Hollick's brother James, who
OL,18,Fwent into the conservatory at around
OL,19,Fmidnight and saw them sleeping.
