OL,6,FAt around 4.30am, Hollick went into
OL,7,Fhis father's bedroom in what
OL,8,Fprosecutors said was a "panicked
OL,9,Fstate", saying that Kairo was not
OL,10,Fbreathing and that he "didn't want to
OL,11,Flose him".
OL,13,FKairo was driven to where Hollick told
OL,14,Fmedical staff he had heard his baby
OL,15,Fson crying before he stopped breathing
OL,16,Fand claimed he only shook him to "wake
OL,17,Fhim up".
